# Test Before Claiming

**Never tell the user something is working or fixed unless you have actually run it and verified.**

- Run the relevant command/script/test before saying "it should work now" or "try again"
- If a fix requires specific env (cluster, API keys) that you cannot satisfy, say so explicitly instead of suggesting it will work
- Prefer testing in this workspace over assuming changes apply correctly
